metadata.description:
$PEPE to the moon and out of this universe! Much love to Not Drake and Not Kanye for all the contributions they put in. If you own this NFT, you will be airdropped a PEPE PFPF Music NFT from the original collection. Below you will find utilities for holding that airdrop:

Utilities include:

Access to a free download of the full PEPE Theme Song

Chances to earn $PEPE for holding the Music NFT based on quantity and rarity held.

WL status for all crypto & web3 related song drops

Free Mint Status On Future PEPE Theme Songs

Learn more about the benefits and utilities by visiting the official page: 
https://aitheartist.squarespace.com/pepemusicnft
